Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] "And so, having\Ncompleted their Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,the two began a journey\Nbeyond severance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,guided by the star of love."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Hey, Mommy, what's\Nyour new book gonna be about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] It's the story\Nof you and your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,the girl who taught\Nus all about Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the last page.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Huh? I don't\Nknow what girl you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NOf course you know what girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:14.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:15.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.91,Main,,0,0,0,,you sang the Love\NSong together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI don't know any girl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kureha. What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've\Nforgotten her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,but also, we loved you\Nfrom the beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,so we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA laughs]\NIt was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you could've seen\Nthe look on Kureha's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect it\Nto feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for choosing\Nme from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You found me, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not a weak girl at the mercy\Nof the Invisible Storm any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm far too important and will\Nnever get excluded, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEAR growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NKuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU humming]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\N♪ Simmer, simmer, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ porridge, simmer,\Nsimmer softly! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Growl, growl, growl! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NAfter Ginko saved her letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-pie gave us official\Npermission to freeload
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,at her house! We're so close\Nnow, Lulu can almost taste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Ginko's gone through a\Nlot, but it seems like it's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,just a matter of time before\Nshe gets her Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO groans]\NI won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never back down on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you protect\NSumika's letter for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, when it cost\Nyou so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Yuri Amour! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NGinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, I'm glad you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want, I can tell\Nyou all about my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you\Ndon't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never, ever\Nbe truly alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And if you don't\Ngive up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Wait, how do\Nyou know those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You are, and have always\Nbeen, my Lady Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Lady Kumaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Like the one from Mom's book?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NDelicious smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You smell, Kureha.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You need to search.\NYou need to find what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] But does what\NI want need to be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI don't know what to look for,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,and I don't know\Nwhere to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI know you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It's in your fingers,\Nin your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NIt's inside you, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, will you give\Nme the Promise Kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NPromise Kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,From me, to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NAnd me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, everything will awaken,\Nand it will all change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO labored breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhoa. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh wow. What a thing to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Growl!\NThe honey porridge is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?\NYou're blushing, Kure-pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Just your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't mind keeping\Nyour eye on Ginko, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,She's sweating a lot. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,My Lady Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[music box plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs] What would\NI dream that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYep! Guess what, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I taught her how to\Nsing the Love Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NOh, my! You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Uh-huh! It's because\Nshe's my special friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,so I figured she\Ngets an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA laughs]\NI see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You really love her,\Ndon't you, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYeah! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Her? Who is "her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:07.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe... Oh. How could\NI forget? I did have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, please help me.\NWho was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting\Nto remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS murmur]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A] I heard\Nthere was another bear attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B] No way!\NWasn't it exterminated, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that girl shot it.\NYou know, what's-her-name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C]\NOh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The one who attracts bad\Nluck to, like, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A] Whether she did\Nor not, I'm telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,another girl from her class\Ntotally got attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,--[STUDENT B] For real?\N--[STUDENT A]  For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C]\NSo, who was it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat? Kaoru Harishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,She was discovered this morning\Nin front of the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,They declared it a bear attack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,based on the poor\Ngirl's injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But how? I thought\NI shot that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means, unfortunately,\Nthere's yet another bear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,still roaming the\Nhalls of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's horrifying. The bears\Ndidn't just take Reia's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.84,Main,,0,0,0,,They stole the\Nproof of our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,They took the star\Npendant I gave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Yuriika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NThe bear with Reia's pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That one is our mortal enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,One day we'll find\Nit, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NAnd then, I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You came here to ask me about\Nsomething, didn't you, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's about an old friend.\NI'd like to know what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.33,Main,,0,0,0,,An old friend, of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. I remembered her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,while I was listening\Nto Mom's music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was younger, apparently\NI had a friend who was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,very special to me.\NI know this girl as "her".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But for some weird reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't remember her\Nface or her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you might know\Nsomething more about my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA grunts]\NCome to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia made a rather\Nstrange comment once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It was shortly before\Nshe died, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,She told me you had suddenly\Nand completely forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,about a close friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:15.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] What else?\NAh yes, her last book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,The Moon Girl and\Nthe Forest Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she wrote\Nthat story about you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,and that forgotten girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom's last book, was\Nabout me and my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGinko, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Sniffle-growl. Your\Nfever's not going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NLulu knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] This'll turn you into\Na nice, cold growl-sicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:47.69,Main,,0,0,0,,and you'll feel way better!\NLulu is so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NKumaria is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,As the world's mother,\Nshe is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,who approves all living\Nthings and gives them love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] The cub who appeared\Nthe day of that silvery blizzard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,was named "Ginko".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,--[KUMACARON grunts] Yo, Ginko!\N--[KUMAMI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an unwanted bear, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.44,Main,,0,0,0,,A lonely Lone-Wolfsbane that'll\Nnever be wanted by anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What, you think you're the\NLone-Wolfsbane princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NKuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] And so,\NGinko was left all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,For obvious reasons,\Nshe became known as
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ginko the Lone Wolfsbane".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:12:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I understand now.\NThis world is ruled by power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No one will ever be\Nkind to the weak ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a dog-eat-dog world,\Nand bear-eat-salmon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMAMI'S MOM]\NKumami! Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMAMI]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMAKO'S MOM]\NKumako! Come back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMAKO]\NUh... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMARY'S MOM]\NKumary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMARY]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMARGARET'S MOM]\NKumargaret!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMARGARET]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMACARON'S MOM]\NKumacaron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMACARON]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMACARON'S MOM laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumacaron, today's your\Nfavorite! Salmon pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I love salmon pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMACARON'S PARENTS laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUMACARON'S DAD]\NYou are just so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Eventually,\Nthe Day of Severance came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Bear cubs in Ginko's\Nsituation were gathered up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,by the superior, Lady Kumaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[LADY KUMASTER]\NRejoice, my children,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,for you have finally been found.\NYes, surely you were unwanted
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,bears, but now you shall be\Ngiven a chance at approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUBS sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.49,Main,,0,0,0,,In this world, only One needs\Nyou and gives you approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We thank her daily for\Nher love and graciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lady Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lady Kumaria"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[LADY KUMASTER] From this day\Nforth, you are cubs of Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You shall be guard-bears\Nand defend the great boundary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,between bear and human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[LADY KUMASTER] Exclude the\Nvermin known as "humans"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.98,Main,,0,0,0,,from our border\Nand eliminate them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,in order to protect our world.\NThat is the mission you shall
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,carry out for us, for\Nwe are the ones loved
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,by the Holy\NMother Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL SOLDIERS yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER A]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL SOLDIER A screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER B]\NHuman excluded, growl-growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER C]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL SOLDIER B screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS]\NHumans excluded, growl-growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER D]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL SOLDIER C screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS]\NHumans excluded, growl-growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[OFFICER GIRL A]\NHQ! HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Request backup immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL SOLDIER D]\NBears excluded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Ginko believed\Nif she fulfilled her mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,surely Kumaria\Nwould approve of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,and she would one\Nday be granted love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I'm not an\Nunwanted Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll keep eating more\Nand more people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,and someday, I'll get approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon enough,\NLady Kumaria will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I'll finally\Nbe granted my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] "There must be an\Namazing world beyond that sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Day after day, the moon girl\Nand the forest girl looked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,at the sky." I wonder if the\Nforest girl must be "her".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,--[LULU] Hello?\N--[KUREHA] Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-pie, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NU-Uh. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl! What book is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a picture book\Nmy mom wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,How cool! May Lulu read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, but I'll warn\Nyou: it doesn't have an ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't it have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NBecause my mom died
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,before she got the\Nchance to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NAw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:58.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NShe was killed by a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. I can check on Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO labored breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko loves you so much,\Nlook at what she's done for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Why?\NWe only just met each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And I haven't done anything for\Nyou. Your injuries and your pain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,should've been mine, but you\Nsacrificed yourself anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER M]\NNo way she's not done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER N]\NEither way, she'd slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS]\NExclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] The animal world is\Nmerciless. The weak, the scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,the ones who can't keep\Nconstant within the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,They are summarily excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NOh, no. It looks like I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Unwanted bear. You are\Na Lone Wolfsbane! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Lone Wolfsbane. So I\Ndon't get to be chosen, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get to be\Napproved by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die here,\Nwithout ever being found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--[GINKO gasps]\N--[music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] This is the love\Nsong my mom taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:58.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nbe alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here now, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NLady Kumaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumaria. From the book.\NYou know it, don't you? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,--Kureha.\N--[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Well, this is great.\NI'm glad you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't go. You were\Nsinging something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Um. I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to go tell\NLulu you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU chuckles]\NIt's almost done! Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginger milk is on its\Nway to completion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu just needs to mix in\Nlots and lots and lots of honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:19:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, the yummy ginger\Nmilk will be all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] There, all done.\NYou two enjoy it together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NOh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You two really love honey\Nginger milk, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]  Yeah! That's because\Nit's the flavor of our love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha? You spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I just remembered it.\NThe ginger milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my Mom made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,And we drank it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave it to me and a friend\Nof mine a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten how that felt.\NA memory can change so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Like now. I feel happy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,--[LULU] Lulu knows why.\N--[KUREHA] Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] It's because of\Nthe honey ginger milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,That's actually\NGinko's love flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the flavor that tells\Nher she's not all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,in the world. That she\Nmatters to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,The taste of a twinkling star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Her love flavor is\Nhoney ginger milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Lulu hasn't added\Nthe honey to finish this off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,yet, so she needs\Nto go get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu will be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,How could I forget a friend\NI cared about so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember now,\Nthat I loved her a lot, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Heh, heh! Honey ginger\Nmilk will get Ginko and Kure-pie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:36.19,Main,,0,0,0,,totally close in no time at all!\N[giggles] Lulu is so clever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah,\NKure-pie's mom's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Moon Girl and\Nthe Forest Girl?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha! Are you\Ntrying to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,the moon girl is\Nsupposed to be Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, would that make\NGinko the forest girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,the worlds were divided\Ninto two parts by the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,There was the moon world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU, SUMIKA]\NAnd the forest world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,'I am sorry, but you\Nmay not,' said Kumaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,for the two worlds have\Nbeen severed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanting to cross that\Nseverance is pride."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on. This is my\Nmother's love song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "There is one way\Nto make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.51,Main,,0,0,0,,If your love is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,your friend will\Nbe waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll find her on the\Nother side of that door."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "Kumaria asked\Nthe two girls a question."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\N"'Is your love the real thing?'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You're "her," aren't you?\NYou're my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl-giggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Lulu's Special Honey\NGinger Milk is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,--[LULU] Growl?\N--[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.37,0:24:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Criminal bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] "Ginko Yurishiro,\NI know all about the grave crime
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:26.17,Main,,0,0,0,,you committed.\NI know what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the one who..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.72,0:24:29.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGinko. Oh, this can't be true!
